    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🔄 LOOPS\n**Status Check Loop**: Continues until scraper job is complete\n**Website Processing Loop**: Processes each restaurant website individually",
        "height": 120,
        "width": 580
      },
      "id": "d56fc086-1748-492f-9b37-6a0a85348f3f",
